\id GAL - Sembeleke Samberigi PNG Galatians 13/2/91 Macnaughtan
\h KAęž‰LEISIA
\toc1 Polomaęž‰ Kaęž‰leisia Siosi paęž‰taęž‰ tapaeyeke wapee
\toc2 Kaęž‰leisia
\toc3 Kaęž‰leisia
\mt1 Polomaęž‰ Kaęž‰leisia Siosi paęž‰taęž‰ tapaeyeke wapee
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 IĚ± Polo IĚ±maęž‰ aposolo hano wi laęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ halimaęž‰ o hali paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ wi na leaęž‰pate mo Yesu Ketisomaęž‰ make mo naku paęž‰taęž‰ ipiki mea daęž‰taeyeke Apaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ make ipiliki telipinaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± wi laęž‰laęž‰me.
\v 2 Do mandake halomaęž‰ kame tonumaęž‰ IĚ± ameĚ±leĚ± apaęž‰tao mo iki Kaęž‰leisia kenke paęž‰taęž‰ haleme siosimanu paęž‰taęž‰ nikaęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰paęž‰laęž‰ pi laęž‰neaasomaęž‰me.
\p 
\v 3 Apaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ make Tekehali Yesu Ketiso ipilikanaęž‰maęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homolo tambaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰eki make puki lopaęž‰niaasaęž‰eki make iki paęž‰taęž‰ kinaęž‰e.
\v 4 Ketisomaęž‰ nikaęž‰ Apaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kakenaęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ nikaęž‰ hoke haunaęž‰ yenkitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ lokemaęž‰ minaęž‰ homeekeme. Kutu pieke ekitaęž‰ do hoke natenaęž‰ halomaęž‰eki paęž‰taęž‰ niki peteluekemaęž‰ piekeme.
\v 5 Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ biki tieke winaęž‰ yeiyaęž‰ latiki latiki pu hamanaęž‰e. Kutu pinaęž‰e.
\s1 Pi seliapotaęž‰ homeke homeke ulaęž‰eki
\p 
\v 6 Aęž‰pei. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ pitelememe alaęž‰eki opitolo IĚ±maęž‰ tolaęž‰tia pominolome. Ikitaęž‰ nate aneke hapu aęž‰ndaęž‰ diaęž‰yaęž‰pate mo hande Ketisonaęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰eki paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ iki wi leaęž‰ Kodaęž‰taęž‰ koto kone minaęž‰paęž‰laaso hataęž‰ pi seliapo maęž‰ndaęž‰ taa miniki haemekaęž‰taęž‰me.
\v 7 Koto pimikaęž‰taęž‰ patetaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ pi seliapotaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ otaęž‰ diaęž‰me hone witolome. Koto alo ekitaęž‰ mandane wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ mo Ketisonaęž‰ otaęž‰ pi seliapo topo topo puluekemaęž‰ taapelememe.
\v 8 Kotaęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰ kone make o mo hepeni nane aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰ enisolomaęž‰ make ambaęž‰ mo nikanaęž‰maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ walomaęž‰ pi seliapomaęž‰ na handeke ataęž‰kaęž‰piki pi seliapo maęž‰ndaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ waleaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kutu piki hau pitaęž‰laęž‰ sometaęž‰ otaęž‰ hoke ti to halaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ mea lopaapeke alee.
\v 9 Ambaęž‰ hande lomaęž‰pate ame IĚ±maęž‰ paa alome. Maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ mo ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ambaęž‰ miniki haeme pi seliapomaęž‰ na handeke taęž‰taęž‰ piki pi aęž‰ndaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ waleaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ kutupiki hau pitaęž‰laęž‰ sometaęž‰ otaęž‰ hoke ti to halaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ mea lopaapeke alee.
\p 
\v 10 Do alo pimaęž‰taęž‰ mo wandaęž‰hali taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰ tiaaluekemaęž‰ alope. Diaęž‰me. Otaęž‰ diaęž‰me. IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homolo paęž‰laęž‰eki weitolome. IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ ya biki daeyaenaęž‰ taapolope. Diaęž‰me. Koto hau puluekemaęž‰ taapoaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ Ketisonaęž‰ e pokaaso hali na hapeke yaęž‰laęž‰me.
\s1 Polo aposolo hali hayeke ekinaęž‰ pi
\p 
\v 11 Ya kametonuo. IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ lakionoe. Kotaęž‰ mo IĚ±maęž‰ walo halo Pi Seliapotaęž‰ kenke haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰ pi diaęž‰me.
\v 12 Kuta make hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ na laku make na walo piaęž‰me. Otaęž‰ Yesu Ketisomaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ peneme yao waleaęž‰me.
\p 
\v 13 IĚ±maęž‰ mo hande Diu tapakenaęž‰ hau miniki haowaęž‰ tomonaęž‰ peaęž‰tiki puaęž‰ hau manunaęž‰ pitaęž‰ ambaęž‰ opu haememe. Kuta IĚ±maęž‰ mo hande Kodaęž‰naęž‰ siosi wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ na homeke tanda halolo hataęž‰ otaęž‰ hoeyaaluekemaęž‰ taapo haowaęž‰me.
\v 14 IĚ±maęž‰ mo hande Diu wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ haumanu muluekemaęž‰taęž‰ ya mandake daeyomaęž‰ Diu wekitonu bepolao lombei pitolo hataęž‰ nikaęž‰ atekenaęž‰ atekenaęž‰ manaęž‰ pimanu hone otaęž‰ wopu uaęž‰me.
\p 
\v 15-16 Kutu puaęž‰pate Kodaęž‰maęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homa tambaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰ hali hataęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ e pokaano ya amaęž‰naęž‰ weleke paęž‰taęž‰ pitono kone IĚ± maĚ±leke liekeme. Kutupa wetepenaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ Yesunaęž‰ Pi Seliapotaęž‰ mo Diu tapake na hake taęž‰taęž‰piki tapakemanu paęž‰taęž‰ walalo ponoyeke Kodaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ eiyeke IĚ± handono waluekemaęž‰ hone pieke di opolo epeeketaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ yaapo pi hotuluekemaęž‰ na pu make
\v 17 mo Diutuseleme nane haemeke titinaęž‰ aposolo haliweki handolo make na peke pa tikitiki mo Aęž‰teibia kenke paęž‰taęž‰ pua wetepetaęž‰ mo Damasikasi da nane paa laęž‰kaęž‰la epoaęž‰me.
\p 
\v 18 Mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ eiyeke IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ peneme yaeyaęž‰ hoki nane bapi tepo hao Diutuseleme da nane pua Pida yaapo pi pi loluekemaęž‰ pula yaaponaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ mandake haopaęž‰me.
\v 19 Koto hataęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ aposolo hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ na handoaęž‰pate pa mo Tekehalinaęž‰ hameke Diaęž‰mesi homeke handoaęž‰me.
\v 20 Do wape pitolo pitaęž‰ otaęž‰ pi alome. Otaęž‰ diki honumakesiki IĚ±maęž‰ yapi alo na loaęž‰me. Otaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ handaęž‰laęž‰me.
\p 
\v 21 Wetepenaęž‰taęž‰ Sitia Silisia kenke yaapo paęž‰taęž‰ hayeke damanu paęž‰taęž‰ poaęž‰me.
\v 22 Koto pitaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo Diudia kenke paęž‰taęž‰ haemeke siosi wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ ya leke popeleketaęž‰ na handemekepate
\v 23 pa mandane wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ mo hande niki paęž‰taęž‰ tanda ku hayaęž‰ somemaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hande hoeyaaluekemaęž‰ taapeaęž‰ haunaęž‰ pi kone ametaęž‰ pa walaęž‰tiki pu halaęž‰me lemeke pi opuataęž‰
\v 24 kotaęž‰ koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ biki yeiyaęž‰ laemekeme.
\c 2
\s1 Aposolo haliwekimaęž‰ Polo ameĚ±leĚ± homeke hone wimikieki
\p 
\v 1 Bapi 14 yapeeke hoki nanetaęž‰ Banabasi yaapo mo Diutuseleme nane Taitasi hatuku paa popaęž‰me.
\v 2 IĚ± ponoyeke Kodaęž‰maęž‰ pue leeke handa poaęž‰me. Kutupa mo siosi you haliweki niki honumake mombela pitaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ mo Diendaili wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ pi seliapo dupa walolome laa la haloaęž‰me. Ya ambaęž‰ pokoaęž‰ e make ame do pokolo e make pa pahameke pokaamaęž‰naęž‰ laa iki paęž‰taęž‰ loaęž‰me.
\v 3 Ya hatuku poaęž‰ some Taitasitaęž‰ Kitiki hali hayekepate mandane tapakemaęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ sekemesaisi hau pinaęž‰e lemekepate kone paeyaomaęž‰ koto hau na peaemekeme.
\v 4 Koto Taitasi sekemesaisi hau pinaęž‰e lemeke tapaketaęž‰ yayapiki pi mimiki haliweki hataęž‰ nikaęž‰ mombololomaęž‰eki handomaęž‰ tiaaluekemaęž‰ aęž‰mbao epemekeme. Nikanaęž‰maęž‰ Yesu Ketiso ameĚ±leĚ± hataęž‰ mo Diu wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ nindi peaasaęž‰ pi wimiki ekimanu nindi na piki kaęž‰laęž‰paęž‰ tapaleke halomaęž‰eki handuluekemaęž‰ kutu pimikime. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ niki mo koto pi ulaęž‰ ekimanu paa nindi wopu peomono loluekemaęž‰yeke hone pimikime.
\v 5 Dikanaęž‰maęž‰ iki Ketiso tapake paęž‰taęž‰ hone witolo hataęž‰ koto tapakemaęž‰ mo otaęž‰ pi seliapo pu hoeyaamaęž‰naęž‰ daĚ±oĚ±la hataęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ waleke hosikisiki maęž‰ndaęž‰ na halopaęž‰me.
\p 
\v 6 Mandane haliwekitaęž‰ biki wiki you hali hake nono pea haemekeme. Ikaęž‰ biki ulaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ pa alee hone witolome. Kodaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ manda yonkelekenaęž‰ hau handa na telipu halaęž‰me. Koto you haliwekimaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ dupiki haumanu apaęž‰tao peaęž‰peke pi maęž‰ndaęž‰ na lememe.
\v 7 Koto hau na pimipate Pidamaęž‰ Diu wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ mo pi seliapo walao haenaęž‰ mea hayeke tupaęž‰ kone Kodaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± make Diu tapake na hake taęž‰taęž‰ piki tapakemanu paęž‰taęž‰ pi walano mea haenaęž‰ leaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ handememe.
\v 8 Pida mo hande Diu wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ aposolo hali mea haenaęž‰ leaęž‰ tupaęž‰ kone IĚ± make Kodaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ welemaęž‰ mo hande Diu na hake taęž‰taęž‰ piki wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ aposolo hali hano mea hayaęž‰me.
\v 9 Diaęž‰mesi Pida make Dioni ikitaęž‰ you haliweki hake nono piki haliweki hataęž‰ mo Kodaęž‰maęž‰ do IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ kaęž‰laęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰piki e handolotaęž‰ niki paeyao homeke tapake halomaęž‰me laa handenaęž‰ walolo Banabasi yaapo kiki minaęž‰ alualu pumaęž‰me. Kutupa nikanaęž‰maęž‰ homeke pi laataęž‰ Banabasi make IĚ± dikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ Diendaili tapake ameĚ±leĚ± hapono ikitaęž‰ Diu tapake ameĚ±leĚ± hamenaęž‰e lomaęž‰me.
\v 10 Kuta ikanaęž‰maęž‰ niki paęž‰taęž‰ honke lemeke pi homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ dupa. Mo niki ameĚ±leĚ± haleme natehali wandaęž‰hali hone na yonkaęž‰lapaęž‰peke lemekeme. Koto honke lemeke hautaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ honkopu hau puaęž‰tiki pu halo hau homekenaęž‰ kone lemekeme.
\s1 Polomaęž‰ Pida tunkiliekeeki
\p 
\v 11 Pida Aęž‰ndioko da nane epeaęž‰ pitaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hautaęž‰ peneme hoi pieke handa IĚ±maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰ tikitiki pua saęž‰saęž‰ puaęž‰me.
\v 12 Diaęž‰mesimaęž‰ tapaeyeke haliweki na opolo epeke haenaęž‰taęž‰ Pidamaęž‰ mo Diendaili Ketiso kametonu ameĚ±leĚ± mandakenaęž‰ pitaęž‰ ne nemekepate pa mo haliweki opolo aęž‰pa haemeketaęž‰ Pidamaęž‰ mo Ketiso tapake paeyao sekemesaisi hau pumanaęž‰e lo haleme tapake haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ paalaęž‰maęž‰ homeke ekinaęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ mo Diendaili Ketiso tapake ameĚ±leĚ± apaęž‰tao pitaęž‰ ne na neke yolaęž‰ tapao pitiekeme.
\v 13 Niki mandakenaęž‰ halomaęž‰ Diu Ketiso kametonu make mo Pidanaęž‰ leke tieke hau honde mimikime. Do koto leke titaęž‰laęž‰ haumaęž‰taęž‰ Banabasi make pa mea tiao peekeme.
\v 14 Koto haliweki ikitaęž‰ mo panake pi seliapomaęž‰ walaęž‰laęž‰ tupaęž‰ tikitiki na pemekeeki handa IĚ±maęž‰ iki paeyaonaęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰ Pida paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Neketaęž‰ Diu hali halepate kone nakanaęž‰maęž‰ Diu hali diaęž‰maęž‰ pa mo Diendaili tapake haleme tupaęž‰ kone haeme. Koto pele ekinaęž‰taęž‰ eki epi tekenaęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ mo Diendaili tapake Diu tapake leke haenaęž‰ tialo alepe.
\s1 Epi amedamaęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulaemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ataęž‰kaęž‰ na piki homeke tupaęž‰ petelelieke
\p 
\v 15 Mo hande Mosesinaęž‰ pi ulaęž‰eki na miniki hake pa haleme Diendaili tapake halememe lo haleme tupaęž‰ diaęž‰me. Nikitaęž‰ otaęž‰ mo Diu tapakemaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰laęž‰ wandaęž‰hali halomaęž‰me.
\v 16 Koto polomaęž‰pate konetaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ hali epimaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ tikitiki yao haluekemaęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ titinaęž‰ peaęž‰peke hautaęž‰ Yesu Ketiso paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulaalimi ekimaęž‰ homeke tikitiki yao halimikie. Pa mo Lo Pi ulaęž‰ ekimanu miniki haleme ekimaęž‰ otaęž‰ diaęž‰me. Koto paęž‰laęž‰eki handolo hataęž‰ niki make Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulaalomaęž‰me. Pa Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ tikitiki yao haluekemaęž‰yeke kutupiki hau otaęž‰ polomaęž‰me. Pate pa mo Mosesinaęž‰ pi ulaęž‰ ekimanu miniki halomaęž‰ ekimaęž‰ diaęž‰me. Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ tikitiki yao haluekemaęž‰taęž‰ hali homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ mo Lo Pi ulaęž‰ ekimanu opua pu halaęž‰ ekimaęž‰ otaęž‰ peaęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰me.
\v 17 Nikitaęž‰ nikaęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ halomaęž‰ ekimaęž‰ nikaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ tikitiki yao haluekemaęž‰ taapolo hataęž‰ kone pa mo Diendaili wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ pu haleme hoke hau leke pulumeeki handaęž‰ wimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ kotoeki maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ handolo hataęž‰taęž‰ koto haumaęž‰taęž‰ Ketisomaęž‰ hoke haumanu wala tiaaso piaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰me lenaęž‰ lomanaęž‰pe. Diaęž‰me. Otaęž‰ diaęž‰me.
\v 18 Kotaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ mo Mosesinaęž‰ pi ulaęž‰ ekimanu pu haleme hau na pulueke laa paeyaowaęž‰ ekimanu paa kini pea pua puaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ mo pi ulaęž‰eki yambolo halo hali peneme halueke.
\v 19 Mo hande pi ulaęž‰eki hotimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo koto pi ulaęž‰eki paęž‰taęž‰ IĚ± ambaęž‰ homa halome. Koto pi ulaęž‰ ekimaęž‰ kone IĚ± homono liaęž‰me. Kutu pieke ekitaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ Kodaęž‰ yaapo daęž‰ta hanoyeke piaęž‰me. IĚ±taęž‰ mo Ketiso homeaęž‰ ti manda mandake homolopaęž‰me.
\v 20 Koto paęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰taęž‰ ame do ya daęž‰ta halo ekitaęž‰ ya kone na daęž‰ta halopate Ketiso IĚ± tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ daęž‰ta halaęž‰me. IĚ±maęž‰ do koto daęž‰ta halo ekitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Eiyeke paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulaalo ekimaęž‰ halome. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ IĚ± daęž‰ta hanoyeke ipikaęž‰ daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ pa haleekeme.
\v 21 Kodaęž‰naęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰eki paęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ kiaaso hataęž‰ mo teaęž‰ hataęž‰ pinaęž‰e pi na lolueke. Pate maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ hone witolo hataęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰ yaapo tikitiki yao haluekemaęž‰ mo pi ulaęž‰eki manumaęž‰ homeke pulueke hone wiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ Ketisotaęž‰ pa homeyaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰me.
\c 3
\s1 Pi ulaęž‰ ekimaęž‰ o hone tulaalomaęž‰ ekimaęž‰
\p 
\v 1 Kaęž‰leisia wandaęž‰halio ikitaęž‰ you hoetaęž‰laęž‰ pate yaęž‰laęž‰me. Epimaęž‰ hoeyao paęž‰laęž‰pe. Mo hande Yesu Ketiso ti manda homeeketaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ikaęž‰ lekemaęž‰ handa honemaęž‰ kone pikisa leke muemenaęž‰yeke ya pimaęž‰ otaęž‰ tikitiki la kuaęž‰me.
\v 2 Ametaęž‰ ya lotaęž‰ pitoloeki homeke domaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ hombo peape. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Sipitiditaęž‰ mo pi ulaęž‰eki manumaęž‰ peaęž‰peke alaęž‰eki opua pimi ekimaęž‰ mimipe o mo pi seliapo opua koto pi paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulaeme ekimaęž‰ mimipe.
\v 3 Ekipa do pambaęž‰ na piki hau pea pelemepe. Ikaęž‰ Ketiso paęž‰taęž‰ daęž‰ta haleme ekitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Sipitidinaęž‰ welemaęž‰ kini peaeyeke yekepate pa ametaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ikaęž‰ lokenaęž‰ welemaęž‰ pu paeyaalimikipe.
\v 4 Holi Sipitidinaęž‰ welemaęž‰ puaęž‰tiki pu haeme hau manutaęž‰ pa ekie hone witemepe. Diaęž‰me. Otaęž‰ hau teke walaęž‰laęž‰me hone witolome.
\v 5 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo pi ulaęž‰eki manumaęž‰ peaęž‰paęž‰peke alaęž‰eki opua puemenaęž‰yeke handa Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ Sipitidi iki paęž‰taęž‰ kiaataęž‰ mo na handeke haumanu iki paęž‰taęž‰ peao halaęž‰pe o mo pi seliapo opua hone tulaamenaęž‰yeke handa kutu pu halaęž‰pe.
\p 
\v 6 Mo hande Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pieke hau hone umanaęž‰e. Mo Baibolomaęž‰ alotaęž‰
\q1 Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulaeyekeme. Koto ipikaęž‰ hone tulaeyekeeki handaataęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ tikitiki piki halie laa handaęž‰ miekeme alaęž‰me.
\m 
\v 7 Kotoeki hone wimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ mo hone tulaleme wandaęž‰hali iki paeyaotaęž‰ otaęž‰ Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰naęž‰ wekiwandiki halaęž‰me hone wiaęž‰paęž‰peke.
\v 8 Baibolomaęž‰ dupa laęž‰ wiekeme Kodaęž‰maęž‰ mo hande Diendaili wandaęž‰hali ikaęž‰ hone tulaleme ekinaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ ipiki ameĚ±leĚ± epea halimikie laa laęž‰ wiekeme. Kotaęž‰ mo Baibolomaęž‰ Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ dupiki pi seliapo la halolo alotaęž‰ Neke paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paeyao wamo pilieke leekeme. Mo koto leeke ekitaęž‰
\v 9 Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰maęž‰ opua hone tulao hayeke handaataęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ wamo piekeeki miekeme. Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulaleme wandaęž‰hali paeyaotaęž‰ Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰maęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ wamo pitaęž‰laęž‰eki mieke tupaęž‰ iki make wamo pea halememe.
\p 
\v 10 Epi amedamaęž‰ mo Lo Pi ulaęž‰eki pitolo ekimaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ± anaęž‰naęž‰ epeaalieke laa hone ti laeyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ esihou pi oto paęž‰taęž‰ halaęž‰me. Kotaęž‰ mo Baibolomaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Epimaęž‰ mo wape pea ulaęž‰ pi ulaęž‰eki paeyao otaęž‰ tanaęž‰ paeyaonaęž‰ opua na pu hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto some epitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ esihou pi yu wia halaęž‰eki oto paęž‰taęž‰ halaęž‰me alaęž‰me.
\v 11 Koto ekitaęž‰ mo Baibolomaęž‰ dupa laęž‰laęž‰me. Hali epimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulaleme ekinaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ epeao ipiki yaapo haenaęž‰ leaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ koto ekimaęž‰ homeke daęž‰ta halieke laęž‰laęž‰eki opuataęž‰ do hone witaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ niki paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ peneme yaęž‰laęž‰me. Maęž‰ndaęž‰ epitaęž‰ mo pi ulaęž‰eki pu haleme ekinaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ epeao ipiki yaapo haenaęž‰ na leaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰me.
\v 12 Pi ulaęž‰ ekimaęž‰ pitaęž‰laęž‰ hau pitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulaasaęž‰ hau yaapotaęž‰ otaęž‰ mandake na pelepeme. Koto paęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰taęž‰ mo Baibolomaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Hali epimaęž‰ mo pi ulaęž‰eki paeyao homeke aęž‰ndaęž‰ na minaęž‰paęž‰lake pu hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ koto sometaęž‰ daęž‰ta halieke alaęž‰me.
\p 
\v 13 Hali epimaęž‰ ti manda endiaeyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto halitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ esihou pi laęž‰laęž‰eki oto paęž‰taęž‰ halaęž‰me mo Baibolonaęž‰ wape pea ulaęž‰ tupaęž‰ Ketisomaęž‰ mo pi ulaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ esihou pi niki paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰paamaęž‰naęž‰yeke ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ nikaęž‰ anketeke mieke handaataęž‰ mo esihou pitaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ yapeekeme.
\v 14 Kutu pieke ekitaęž‰ mo hande Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ Neke tambaęž‰ mulueke laa laęž‰ wieke pimaęž‰taęž‰ Yesu Ketiso paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ mo Diendaili wandaęž‰hali make tambaęž‰ meaataęž‰ kotaęž‰ niki make Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulaaso hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi laęž‰ wiaęž‰ Sipitidi miomono piekeme.
\s1 Pi ulaęž‰ ekimaęž‰ o pi laęž‰ ulaęž‰ ekimaęž‰
\p 
\v 15 Kame tonuo. Ametaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ mo hande nate paeyao pu halomaęž‰ hau maęž‰ndaęž‰ minolome. Hali yaapomaęž‰ hau maęž‰ndaęž‰ puluekemaęž‰ dupupanaęž‰e laa pi laęž‰ witolo hataęž‰ toopi mini pikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ipilikaęž‰ ipilikaęž‰ kone maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ koto pi laęž‰ witelepeeki tunkula make hau maęž‰ndaęž‰ na apaęž‰taapeke yelieke.
\v 16 Kodaęž‰maęž‰ make koto tupaęž‰ kone Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ make ipikaęž‰ hoki nane epolo pieke hali paęž‰taęž‰ make ipikaęž‰ pi laęž‰ witaęž‰laęž‰eki manumaęž‰ laęž‰ wiekeme. Baibolomaęž‰ hoki nane epolo pieke haliweki alaęž‰ pinaęž‰ teketaęž‰ haliweki eleke eleke laa na alaęž‰pate pa hoki nane epolo pieke hali alaęž‰ pinaęž‰ teketaęž‰ hali homeke homeke la alaęž‰me. Mo koto hali bikitaęž‰ Ketisoe.
\v 17 IĚ±maęž‰ do alo pinaęž‰ teketaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰ yaapo homeke hone witolo hataęž‰ otaęž‰ handeteke halueke laa Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pi laęž‰ wiekeme. Koto ekinaęž‰ mo hande 430 bapi wetepetaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ Mosesi paęž‰taęž‰ haleeke pi ulaęž‰eki manumaęž‰ mo ambaęž‰ Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ laęž‰ wieke pitaęž‰ otaęž‰ na yambolo na paeyao peaęž‰peke yeekeme.
\v 18 Mo hande Kodaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kitaęž‰laęž‰ ale meaęž‰peke teketaęž‰ mo hande Lo Pi ulaęž‰ ekimanu pea meaęž‰peke yaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ kototaęž‰ mo Kodaęž‰maęž‰ laęž‰ witolo hataęž‰ kulueke laa laęž‰ wiekeeki tekenaęž‰ na pitememe. Pate Kodaęž‰maęž‰ Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ pi laęž‰ wiekeeki paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ haleekeme.
\p 
\v 19 Kutu piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo hande Mosesinaęž‰ pi ulaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ eki pinaęž‰ la haleekepe. Koto pi ulaęž‰eki manutaęž‰ mo ambaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ laęž‰ wiekeeki taapunaęž‰ apaęž‰tao wiki hautaęž‰ mo hoke hoke haumanu peneme yao waluekemaęž‰ wiekeme. Koto pi ulaęž‰eki manutaęž‰ pa u pelia pua mo hande Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰naęž‰ hoki nane epolo pieke hali ipikitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ambaęž‰ pi laęž‰ wieke hali opolo ipulutaęž‰ paeyaenaęž‰e. Mo Lo Pi ulaęž‰eki manutaęž‰ homeke hali kaęž‰pa paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ enisolo tonumaęž‰ halaęž‰niaeyekeme.
\v 20 Pate homekenaęž‰ pi laluekemaęž‰ kaęž‰pa hali hataęž‰ e pokaapeke na yaęž‰laęž‰me. Kutupa Kodaęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ otaęž‰ homeke halaęž‰me.
\s1 Pi ulaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ teketaęž‰
\p 
\v 21 Koto alo ekinaęž‰taęž‰ mo pi ulaęž‰eki manumaęž‰taęž‰ mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi laęž‰ ulaęž‰eki hoeyaaluekemaęž‰ wia paęž‰laęž‰pe. Diaęž‰me. Otaęž‰ diaęž‰me. Mo pi ulaęž‰eki homekemaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali daęž‰taapeke yaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ yolutaęž‰ kotaęž‰ kototaęž‰ paeyaomaęž‰ koto pi ulaęž‰eki opua miniki hataęž‰ Kodaęž‰ yaapo tikitiki halo pimipate
\v 22 pa mo Baibolomaęž‰ alotaęž‰ kenke paeyaotaęž‰ hoke haunaęž‰ wele oto paęž‰taęž‰ ulaęž‰me alaęž‰me. Koto ekinaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ mo Yesu Ketiso paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulalemeeki tekenaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ kulueke laa laęž‰ uaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ mo hone tulaaso haleme wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ halo halaęž‰me.
\p 
\v 23 Ambaęž‰ mo hande hone tulaasaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ nate aĚ±iĚ± na epeaęž‰ tomaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ mo Lo Pi ulaęž‰eki manumaęž‰ niki paeyao dipula mea mo koto epolo paęž‰laęž‰ hone tulaasaęž‰eki peneme yaenaęž‰ hoĚ±lindaęž‰ pu pamba hayaęž‰me.
\v 24 Koto ekinaęž‰ mo hone tulaasaęž‰ hau paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ yaapo tikitiki yao hamono mo Lo Pi ulaęž‰ ekimaęž‰ niki handeteke hatiki puaataęž‰ Ketiso ipulu kinaeyekeme.
\v 25 Kotaęž‰ ametaęž‰ mo hone tulaasaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ nate opolo aęž‰paęž‰leke handaataęž‰ mo Lo Pi ulaęž‰eki manumaęž‰ niki pa na handeteke halaęž‰me.
\p 
\v 26 Iki paeyaotaęž‰ hone tulaasaęž‰eki paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ Yesu Ketiso ameĚ±leĚ± apaęž‰tao Kodaęž‰naęž‰ wekiwandiki halememe.
\v 27 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ Ketiso ameĚ±leĚ± taęž‰maęž‰ni pea hamenaęž‰yeke bapitaisi peayaęž‰me. Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ ametaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ Ketisonaęž‰ daęž‰taasaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ akaęž‰ leke pambao halememe.
\v 28 Koto paęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo Diu tapake pitaęž‰ Diendaili tapake yaapo make ataęž‰kaęž‰ na pu mo e handeteke halaęž‰ haliweki pitaęž‰ e pokaasaęž‰ haliweki yaapo make ataęž‰kaęž‰ na pu mo wandaęž‰ pitaęž‰ hali yaapo make ataęž‰kaęž‰ na pu piki iki paeyaotaęž‰ Yesu Ketiso ameĚ±leĚ± apaęž‰tao otaęž‰ homeke tapake halememe.
\v 29 Ikitaęž‰ Ketiso ipikaęž‰eki haemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ikitaęž‰ mo Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰naęž‰ hoki nane wandaęž‰hali hataęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ kulueke laa pi laęž‰ wiekeeki milimikie.
\c 4
\p 
\v 1 Mo koto pi honiki kone panake laęž‰ moneaaso pitaęž‰ dupa. Mo atekenaęž‰ anketeke mulu polo paęž‰laęž‰ weki homeketaęž‰ panake daetolo halaęž‰ dinaęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ mo pa hameke e pokaasaęž‰ hali leke mea hasaęž‰me.
\v 2 Mo ipikaęž‰ apaęž‰naęž‰ mu hake alemanu paeyaotaęž‰ otaęž‰ ipikaęž‰eki yaęž‰laęž‰pate kone ipikaęž‰ atekemaęž‰ laęž‰ ulaęž‰ nate epenaęž‰ molu halaęž‰ tomaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ mo ipikaęž‰ loke handeteke halaęž‰ halimaęž‰ kone mo ipikaęž‰ alemanu make handeteke hao hawalieke.
\v 3 Niki make koto tupaęž‰ wekiwandiki leke hataęž‰ do kenkenaęž‰ teke na wiki manaęž‰ pimanu oto paęž‰taęž‰ haomaęž‰pate
\v 4 pa mo hande Kodaęž‰naęž‰ laęž‰ wieke nate otaęž‰ opolo epeeke pitaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ weki kone tapaeyekeme. Koto wekitaęž‰ mo do kenke wandaęž‰naęž‰ weki tupaęž‰ aęž‰paataęž‰
\v 5 mo Lo Pi wiekeeki oto paęž‰taęž‰ haemeke wandaęž‰hali peteluekemaęž‰ koto Diu tapakenaęž‰ pi wiekeeki oto paęž‰taęž‰ hayekeme. Niki Kodaęž‰naęž‰ wekiwandiki hamono kutu piekeme.
\p 
\v 6 Ikitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ wekiwandiki haleme ekinaęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wekinaęž‰ Sipitiditaęž‰ nikaęž‰ puki paęž‰taęž‰ pitinaęž‰ tapaeyaęž‰me. Mo Apaęž‰o. Ya Apaęž‰o lo halaęž‰ Sipitiditaęž‰ niki paęž‰taęž‰ tapaeyaęž‰me.
\v 7 Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ ikitaęž‰ pa hameke e pokaaseme wandaęž‰hali na halemepate ipikaęž‰ wekiwandiki halememe. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wekiwandiki haleme ekinaęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wekiwandikinaęž‰ wi alaęž‰ alemanu iki kilieke.
\s1 Polomaęž‰ Kaęž‰leisia siosi paęž‰taęž‰ hone tieke wiekeeki
\p 
\v 8 Ambaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ haumanu na handemeke ekimaęž‰taęž‰ ikitaęž‰ pa mo hande otaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ diaęž‰yeke yayapiki ale manunaęž‰ e pokao haemekeme.
\v 9 Kutu pimipate ametaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ Kodaęž‰ handelememe o diaęž‰me ametaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ iki handaęž‰laęž‰me lapeke yaęž‰laęž‰me. Koto paęž‰laęž‰pate pa ekipa mo hoke honkopu na hake kenke tumbao haleme temokomanu paęž‰taęž‰ paa laęž‰kaęž‰la pua ikaęž‰ pa hameke e pokaaseme wandaęž‰hali kone haluekemaęž‰ taapo halemepe.
\v 10 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo nate tiekemanu paęž‰taęž‰ make o walaęž‰ pankaęž‰laęž‰ sumbaęž‰manu paęž‰taęž‰ make o di mapemanu paęž‰taęž‰ make o panake bapi ipulaęž‰ ekimanu paęž‰taęž‰ make koto nate manunaęž‰ di tunkulaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ hone wopu u halememe.
\v 11 Ikaęž‰ piteme haunaęž‰ IĚ± paalaęž‰maęž‰ ambaęž‰ homolome. Pa ekipeke. IĚ±maęž‰ iki tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ pokoaęž‰ etaęž‰ pa pahameke pokonope hone witolo alome.
\p 
\v 12 Kametonuo. Ikitaęž‰ IĚ± tupaęž‰ hamenaęž‰yeke IĚ±maęž‰ iki honke alome. IĚ± make ikimaęž‰ handeke some kone halome. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ hoke hau maęž‰ndaęž‰ na pelememe.
\v 13 IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ pi kini pea waloaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ teketaęž‰ mo hande IĚ±maęž‰ yeni muaęž‰ ekimaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa hataęž‰ pi waloaęž‰me. Kutu puaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ hone wilimime.
\v 14 Koto hande ya lokenaęž‰ hoke yeni hayaęž‰ ekimaęž‰ iki kaęž‰ndaęž‰ tieke peaeyaęž‰pate kone ikanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± na kiao make na tolu limime. Koto hau na pikitaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ mo hande Kodaęž‰naęž‰ enisolo leke handaęž‰ mimime o pa Yesu Ketiso kone leke IĚ± handaęž‰ mimime.
\v 15 Koto pitaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰ tieke wopu wiaęž‰me. Pate pa ametaęž‰ ekipa paęž‰laęž‰pe. IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ dupiki pi kone lapeke yaęž‰laęž‰me. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± tambaęž‰ muluekemaęž‰ ikaęž‰ leke yokaęž‰ mea kiaęž‰peke yaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ yolutaęž‰ ambaęž‰ yokaęž‰ mea kulu pimime.
\v 16 Pate ametaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ mo otaęž‰ pi la kitolo ekimaęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ tunkuliki hali halope.
\p 
\v 17 Mo hande iki paęž‰taęž‰ homu pea hake nono peleme haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ hone wopu u halemepate ikaęž‰ wetepe pulueke hone u haleme ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ epekeeki diaęž‰me. Ikaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ IĚ± iki ameĚ±leĚ± haloeki tekili peaaluekemaęž‰ taapelememe. Kotaęž‰ mo ikanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ hone witemeeki pao iki paęž‰taęž‰ homeke hone uemenaęž‰yeke pitememe.
\v 18 Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ hone witolo epeke haumanu puluekemaęž‰ hone wopu wiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ kototaęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰me. Nate maęž‰ndaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ IĚ± haowaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ make na haowaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ make kutupiki haumanu pimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰me.
\v 19 Ya wekiwandiki sunuo. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ Ketisonaęž‰ hau muemenaęž‰yeke amaęž‰maęž‰ weki taapolo pilaęž‰ tupaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ iki paa taapolo hataęž‰ tanda muaęž‰tiki pulume.
\v 20 Hone maęž‰ndaęž‰ uluekemaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ iki ameĚ±leĚ± mandake hawee hone wotu ulaęž‰me. Koto ekimaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ hone eleke eleke wopu witolome.
\s1 Seta Heika yaaponaęž‰ hau mandaęž‰ meaasaęž‰eki
\p 
\v 21 Iki ameĚ±leĚ± mandane wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ mo Mosesinaęž‰ pi ulaęž‰eki manunaęž‰ oto paęž‰taęž‰ hao haluekemaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰ tapake iki paęž‰taęž‰ dupiki pi lotaęž‰ pionoe - mo hande pi ulaęž‰ ekimaęž‰ alaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ opitemepe.
\v 22 Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰maęž‰ weki yaapo mendiekeme laęž‰laęž‰me. Weki maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ pa hameke e pokaeyeke wandaęž‰maęž‰ mendiekeme. Weki maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ kaęž‰laęž‰paęž‰ tapao hataęž‰ halinaęž‰ da peeke wandaęž‰maęž‰ mendiekeme.
\v 23 Mo hande pa hameke e pokaeyeke wandaęž‰maęž‰ mendieke wekitaęž‰ paeyaomaęž‰ mondu halaęž‰ tupaęž‰ mendiekeme. Pate mo hande kaęž‰laęž‰paęž‰ tapao hataęž‰ hali peeke wandaęž‰maęž‰ mendieke wekitaęž‰ koto wekitaęž‰ mo hande Kodaęž‰maęž‰ laęž‰ wiekeeki yaenaęž‰ yeke handa mendiekeme.
\v 24 Do hau yaapomaęž‰taęž‰ mo mandaęž‰ meaasaęž‰eki hone u tiaasaęž‰me. Mo wandaęž‰ yaapotaęž‰ mo laęž‰ u alu pieke pi yaapo tupaęž‰e. Mo pi laęž‰ wiekeeki maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ Sainai pote paęž‰taęž‰ kini pea haleekeme. Koto haleeke laęž‰ witaęž‰laęž‰ pinaęž‰ wekiwandikitaęž‰ pa hameke e pokaasaęž‰ wekiwandiki haemekeme.
\v 25 Mo hande pa hameke e pokaasaęž‰ wandaęž‰ Heika ipikitaęž‰ mo hande Sainai pote tupaęž‰e lapeke yaęž‰laęž‰me. Kutupa Sainaitaęž‰ mo Aęž‰teibia kenke paęž‰taęž‰ halaęž‰ potetaęž‰ mo hande pa ulaęž‰ Diutuseleme daoni tupaęž‰e lapeke yaęž‰laęž‰me. Koto Diutuselemetaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali tonkaęž‰naęž‰ pa hameke e pokaasememe.
\v 26 Koto paęž‰laęž‰pate mo hepeni nane ulaęž‰ Diutuseleme maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ kaęž‰laęž‰paęž‰ tapao halaęž‰me. Kotaęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ nikaęž‰ amaęž‰ halaęž‰me.
\v 27 Kotoeki mo Baibolomaęž‰ alotaęž‰
\q1 Mo weki diaęž‰yaęž‰laęž‰ wandaęž‰o. Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰peke.
\q1 Kutupa mo weki taapolo tanda pitaęž‰laęž‰eki hone na wiki wandaęž‰o.
\q1 Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ eĚ± wi lapeke.
\q1 Mo halimaęž‰ kiaeyeke wandaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wekiwandiki wopu pa mo halikimaęž‰ epeke tupaęž‰ handeteke hao hayaęž‰ wandaęž‰ lombei peao mendilieke laęž‰laęž‰me.
\p 
\v 28 Ya kametonuo. Ikitaęž‰ mo hande laęž‰ wieke ekinaęž‰ mendieke weki Aisaęž‰ke tupaęž‰ kone iki make Kodaęž‰maęž‰ laęž‰ wieke ekinaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wekiwandiki halememe.
\v 29 Koto hande pitaęž‰me mo hande wandaęž‰ paeyaomaęž‰ mondu halaęž‰ tupaęž‰ mendieke wekimaęž‰taęž‰ mo hande Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Sipitidimaęž‰ peayeke mendieke weki kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ homaeyeke tupaęž‰ ame make koto homeke hau pu halaęž‰me.
\v 30 Pate pa mo Baibolomaęž‰taęž‰ eki alaęž‰pe. Dupa alaęž‰me. Mo pahameke e pokaasaęž‰ wandaęž‰ make ipikaęž‰ weki tonkaęž‰naęž‰ panane halo paęž‰naęž‰ tapaapeke. Pa ekipeke. Mo kutupiki wekimaęž‰taęž‰ mo hande kaęž‰laęž‰paęž‰ tapao halaęž‰ wandaęž‰naęž‰ weki tupaęž‰ hataęž‰ mo hande apaęž‰naęž‰ anketeke putupaalu peaęž‰peke na yelieke laęž‰laęž‰me.
\v 31 Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ kametonuo. Nikitaęž‰ mo pahameke e pokaasaęž‰ wandaęž‰naęž‰ wekiwandiki diaęž‰yaęž‰laęž‰pate nikitaęž‰ mo kaęž‰laęž‰paęž‰ tapaalaęž‰ wandaęž‰naęž‰ wekiwandiki halomaęž‰me.
\c 5
\s1 Kaęž‰laęž‰paęž‰ tapao halaęž‰ haunaęž‰ pi
\p 
\v 1 Otaęž‰ kaęž‰laęž‰paęž‰ tapao hamono Ketisomaęž‰ niki kaęž‰laęž‰paęž‰ tapaalaęž‰me. Koto paęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰taęž‰ kaęž‰laęž‰paęž‰ tapaalaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali tupaęž‰ takaęž‰lao hataęž‰ mo pa hameke e pokaaseme wandaęž‰hali tupaęž‰ paa na hapaęž‰peke.
\p 
\v 2 Opuaęž‰paęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ Polomaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ do pi alome. Ikitaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ sekemesaisi hau pinaęž‰ lemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ Ketisotaęž‰ otaęž‰ pa ale leke haenaęž‰ lelimikie.
\v 3 Hoto yaapo peao paa kinki pitolo IĚ±maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ ipiki sekemesaisi hau pinaęž‰ leaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto halitaęž‰ mo hande Lo Pi ulaęž‰eki paeyaonaęž‰ oto paęž‰taęž‰ homeke hao halieke.
\v 4 Mo iki ameĚ±leĚ± haleme mandane hali wekimaęž‰taęž‰ mo Lo Pi ulaęž‰eki paeyao pitolo ekimaęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰ yaapo epea haluekemaęž‰ taapo haemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kutu piteme haliwekitaęž‰ ikaęž‰ Ketiso ameĚ±leĚ± halo peleme ekitaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone ti paleke leke laęž‰kaęž‰laęž‰ mea baasememe. Kutu pimi ekimaęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone Kodaęž‰naęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homa tambaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰eki tikene halememe.
\v 5 Nikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ niki tikitiki yaenaęž‰ yeke ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ ti lao halomaęž‰me. Do hautaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ Holi Sipitidinaęž‰ welemaęž‰ nikaęž‰ hone tulaasomaęž‰eki paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ peaalieke hone wia hone bao halomaęž‰me.
\v 6 Niki Yesu Ketiso paęž‰taęž‰ tunao haomaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ sekemesaisi hau pitaęž‰laęž‰eki make sekemesaisi hau na pitaęž‰laęž‰eki make koto hau telipinaęž‰taęž‰ pa pa alemaęž‰ handaęž‰laęž‰me. Pate hone tulaaso hataęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homaęž‰ alualu pu haemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto hautaęž‰ otaęž‰ekie.
\p 
\v 7 Ikitaęž‰ otaęž‰ epeke tupaęž‰ aĚ±iĚ±ya pu haemepate pa ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ otaęž‰ pimanu opua peaamaęž‰naęž‰ epimaęž‰ alekemaęž‰ iki haĚ±laĚ±ęž‰mbe liaaso piaęž‰pe. Ekipa ikaęž‰ hone laęž‰kaęž‰laeyaęž‰pe.
\v 8 Kutu piki hautaęž‰ mo hande iki wi laęž‰laęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ na peayaęž‰me.
\v 9 Mo hande palaowa pombei yaasaęž‰ yisiti sikimaęž‰taęž‰ mo palaowa paeyao kone pombei yelieke alemepate
\v 10 pa ya honemaęž‰ handolo ekitaęž‰ nikitaęž‰ mo Tekehali paęž‰taęž‰ tunao halomeke handa ikanaęž‰maęž‰ hone maęž‰ndaęž‰ na wiki pa IĚ±maęž‰ witolo hone kone anaęž‰naęž‰ wilimikie hone ulume. Kutupa mo ikaęž‰ hone laęž‰kaęž‰laasaęž‰ halitaęž‰ epipe. Pa ipikitaęž‰ epi yaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ make mo ipikaęž‰ kutu pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hoke yenki anaęž‰naęž‰ halieke.
\p 
\v 11 Ya kame tonuo. Mandane haliwekimaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ aleme pitaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ mo sekemesaisi hau pumanaęž‰ pipe laa pa walaęž‰tia pu haowaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ pa ekipeke ikanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± pa kaęž‰ndaęž‰ peao halemepe. Koto aleme pitaęž‰ otaęž‰ pi yaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ yolutaęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo ya Ketisonaęž‰ aęž‰kaęž‰tei wape piki tinaęž‰ pi walaaso ekimaęž‰taęž‰ iki hoke hone na u tialo piaęž‰me.
\v 12 Ya hone paęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ mo ikaęž‰ hone laęž‰kaęž‰la tiaaseme haliweki ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone sekemesaisi pimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ pa koto hau homeke na piki pa ikaęž‰ tukiliki tonkaęž‰naęž‰ minaęž‰e.
\p 
\v 13 Ya kame tonuo. Ametaęž‰ ikinaęž‰ do tupaęž‰ alome. Ikitaęž‰ kaęž‰laęž‰paęž‰ tapao haleme haliweki hamenaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ wi laęž‰laęž‰me. Koto paęž‰laęž‰pate ikaęž‰ honemaęž‰ nikitaęž‰ kaęž‰laęž‰paęž‰ tapao halomaęž‰me hone witolo pa mo hande lokenaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰ ambaęž‰ hau manumaęž‰ neke na handeteke haenaęž‰ lapaęž‰peke. Kotoeki na pikitaęž‰ pa ikaęž‰ kametonu ameĚ±leĚ± pukimaęž‰ homeleme ekimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone tambaęž‰ mu alualu puemenaęž‰ lenaęž‰ lapaęž‰peke.
\v 14 Mo hande Lo Pi ulaęž‰eki paeyao apaęž‰tao hone wiomonotaęž‰ kotaęž‰ pa pa ulumaęž‰ pi homeke homeke ulaęž‰me. Dupa. Nakaęž‰ kone pukimaęž‰ homele tupaęž‰ kotaęž‰ nakaęž‰ yankeketonu paęž‰taęž‰ make pukimaęž‰ homaęž‰paęž‰peke laa la ulaęž‰me.
\v 15 Koto la ulaęž‰pate ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ikaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone ape aęž‰ndaęž‰ leke yokaalu alu pu haemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ya some hombo koto pimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ otaęž‰ wopu handeteke hapaęž‰peke. Ikaęž‰ tapake ameĚ±leĚ± kone epeke tupaęž‰ pataęž‰ pea na hake otaęž‰ tekili tekili pu hoeyaalimikie.
\s1 Holi Sipitidinaęž‰ hau lokenaęž‰ hau yaapo
\p 
\v 16 IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ dupiki pi alome. Mo Sipitidimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ pu haleme haumanu kilu tombuao handeteke hataęž‰ tikitiki yawaenaęž‰ lapaęž‰peke. Kutu pimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo ikaęž‰ lokemaęž‰ naęž‰naęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰ hau manutaęž‰ na telia pilimikie.
\v 17 Pa ekipeke alo mo lokenaęž‰ haumaęž‰taęž‰ mo Holi Sipitidi bepolaluekemaęž‰ taapo halaęž‰me. Kutupa make mo Holi Sipitidimaęž‰taęž‰ mo lokenaęž‰ haumanu bepolaluekemaęž‰ taapo pu halaęž‰me. Koto hau yaapomaęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ lu alu pu halepeme. Koto pitepe ekimaęž‰taęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo puluekemaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰ hau piaęž‰peke ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ peaęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰me.
\v 18 Koto paęž‰laęž‰pate kotaęž‰ mo Sipitidimaęž‰ iki hatuku pu hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo Lo Pi ulaęž‰ ekimaęž‰taęž‰ iki na tombuao halaęž‰me.
\p 
\v 19 Mo lokenaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰ haunaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰ hautaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ handa hone wilimime. Koto hau manutaęž‰ doe. Tooli kaęž‰taasaęž‰ hau o yolaęž‰laęž‰ hau o suseke suseke haasaęž‰ hau
\v 20 o toopi ti wepia ulaęž‰ ale paęž‰taęž‰ yeni pitaęž‰laęž‰ hau o peteke peteke hau o aęž‰ndaęž‰ tunkulaęž‰laęž‰ hau o mineke pankaęž‰laęž‰ hau o maęž‰ndaęž‰ tombualuekemaęž‰ hoke hone witaęž‰laęž‰eki make o maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ ale paęž‰taęž‰ we pambaęž‰laęž‰eki make o ti teke yokaęž‰laęž‰ hau o ape ape lo tapake tekili pitaęž‰laęž‰ hau
\v 21 o maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ epeke haunaęž‰ mineke pankaęž‰laęž‰eki make o ikali naa keaasaęž‰eki make o kimaęž‰ na homeke hoke ikali nalaęž‰ haumanu make kutupiki mandane hau maęž‰ndaęž‰manu make hone wilimime. Ambaęž‰ iki kinki puaęž‰ tupaęž‰ ame make paa kinki pitolome. Do alo haumanu pu haleme wandaęž‰hali ikitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰eki paęž‰taęž‰ puaęž‰peke na yelieke.
\p 
\v 22 Koto paęž‰laęž‰pate mo Holi Sipitidimaęž‰taęž‰ epeke haumanu dupa peawaasaęž‰me. Pukimaęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ hau make puki tukiki nane otaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ hau make puki lopaasaęž‰ hau make homu pea yu wia halaęž‰ hau make aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homolo epeke pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ tambaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰ hau make hone tulao hataęž‰ e pokaęž‰laęž‰ hau make
\v 23 kimelemaęž‰ halaęž‰ hau make nakaęž‰ kone nakaęž‰ loke hone yaapo lu tombuao halaęž‰ hau make ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ koto hau paeyao peawaasaęž‰me. Dupiki haumanu saęž‰saęž‰ puluekemaęž‰ Lo Pi maęž‰ndaęž‰ otaęž‰ na ulaęž‰me.
\v 24 Mo Yesu Ketisonaęž‰ wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ lokenaęž‰ hau make koto loke ipikaęž‰ namonamo hataęž‰ naęž‰naęž‰ naęž‰naęž‰ pitolo loke tiaasaęž‰eki make koto hau paeyaotaęž‰ Ketiso yaapo apaęž‰tao mo aęž‰kaęž‰tei wape piki tinaęž‰ lia endialememe.
\p 
\v 25 Mo Holi Sipitidimaęž‰taęž‰ nikaęž‰ daęž‰ta halomaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ teke haleke handaataęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo do halomaęž‰eki make Holi Sipitidimaęž‰ kone tombuao haenaęž‰ lomanaęž‰ peaęž‰peke alee.
\v 26 Nikanaęž‰maęž‰ hakoko litaęž‰laęž‰ hau na pu make maęž‰ndaęž‰ sokaęž‰laęž‰ homenaęž‰ loluekemaęž‰ toyaęž‰ toyaęž‰ piki haumanu na pu make IĚ± miaęž‰peke alee laa honemaęž‰ honditi pu alualu pilaęž‰ hau make paeyao na pumanaęž‰e.
\c 6
\s1 Tambaęž‰ mu alualu pitaęž‰laęž‰ hau
\p 
\v 1 Ya kametonuo. Maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ hoke hau pitolo haenaęž‰ handemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ iki epitaęž‰ mo Holi Sipitidimaęž‰ tumbiki some hombo ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo some mea tiao haenaęž‰ alotaęž‰ otaęž‰ yopu siki piaęž‰paęž‰peke. Kuta make mo hande ipiki mea lopaeyaęž‰ haumaęž‰ iki make yolaęž‰ mea lopaamaęž‰naęž‰ wopu handeteke hataęž‰ piaęž‰paęž‰peke.
\v 2 Ikaęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu ikaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone tambaęž‰ mu alualu peaęž‰paęž‰peke. Kutu piki hau pilimi ekimaęž‰taęž‰ Ketisonaęž‰ pi la ulaęž‰ ekimaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰eki telielememe.
\v 3 Iki tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ biki na wiliaęž‰ some haliepate kone IĚ±taęž‰ biki ulaęž‰me hone wiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ koto somemaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kone makeaasaęž‰me.
\v 4 Ikaęž‰ piteleme hau manutaęž‰ ikaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone ikaęž‰ honemaęž‰ telipa handaęž‰paęž‰peke. Homeke halimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ hau piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ otaęž‰ haunaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ kutu piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ pitaęž‰laęž‰ haunaęž‰taęž‰ hoelaęž‰maęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰maęž‰ laa na hando telipu hapeke yelieke.
\v 5 Hali homeke homekemaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰eki ipikaęž‰ kone mea tu hapeke yelieke.
\p 
\v 6 Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi walaęž‰laęž‰eki opua minaęž‰laęž‰ somemaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰ alemanu ipikaęž‰ walaęž‰laęž‰ hali yaapo putupa alu piaęž‰paęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me.
\p 
\v 7 Ikaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone na makeaapaęž‰peke. Kodaęž‰ makeake hau peaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰ some maęž‰ndaęž‰ otaęž‰ na halaęž‰me. Wae nokaęž‰paęž‰laęž‰ somemaęž‰ otaęž‰ mo ipikaęž‰ nokaęž‰paęž‰laęž‰ waenaęž‰ kiliki kone talaęž‰peke yelieke.
\v 8 Mo somemaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ lokenaęž‰ namonamo paęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ waemanu ti lao nokaęž‰peaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto namo namonaęž‰ kilikitaęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰eki milieke. Pate ipikaęž‰ waetaęž‰ mo Holi Sipitidimaęž‰ kilu tombuao halaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ wae noko peaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo ipikaęž‰ talaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ mo hande Holi Sipitidimaęž‰ kitaęž‰laęž‰ deto halaęž‰eki milieke.
\v 9 Kutu peaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰taęž‰ mo epeke haumanu pu haluekemaęž‰ kimaęž‰ na homo hamanaęž‰e. Mo hau aęž‰ndaęž‰ na minaęž‰paęž‰laomaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto haunaęž‰ kiliki talaęž‰peke natetaęž‰ opolo ipilieke.
\v 10 Wandaęž‰hali paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ epeke hau piaęž‰peke ekinaęž‰ waleke aęž‰ndaęž‰ opolo epeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ epeke hau otaęž‰ piaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me. Kutu piaęž‰peke yolo paęž‰laęž‰pate mo nikaęž‰ Ketiso tapakenaęž‰ haleme wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ hone otaęž‰ wopu witolo hataęž‰ tambaęž‰ meaęž‰tiki peaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me.
\s1 Polomaęž‰ Yesu homeeke kolosunaęž‰ hone wopu wiekeeki
\p 
\v 11 Do ya kikimaęž‰ kone laaso wape tieke handaęž‰pe.
\v 12 Mo ikanaęž‰maęž‰ sekemesaisi hau puemenaęž‰ yeke ti aleme wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ biki mea aęž‰meiyaaso hataęž‰ kone pa mo yonkeleke manda pitaęž‰laęž‰ haunaęž‰ hakoko liki pimanu loluekemaęž‰ yeke alememe. Kutu pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo Yesu homeeke kolosunaęž‰ pi walaemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ mandane Diu tapakemaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰ halaamaęž‰naęž‰ yeke pa yanaaso do manda yonkelekenaęž‰ pitaęž‰laęž‰ hau pu halememe.
\v 13 Mo koto sekemesaisi hau pu haleme wandaęž‰hali ikanaęž‰maęž‰ kone pa mo Lo Pi ulaęž‰ ekimanu paeyaotaęž‰ na telia pu halememe. Mo haliwekimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ sekemesaisi hau puemenaęž‰ yeke hone peleme ekinaęž‰ ikaęž‰ biki daeyaenaęž‰ yeke pitememe.
\v 14 Kutu pu halemepate IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ mo nikaęž‰ Tekehali Yesu Ketiso mo kolosunaęž‰ homeeke ekinaęž‰ homeke hakoko liki pi lolueke. Yesu Ketisomaęž‰ kolosunaęž‰ homeeke handa ya hone paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ do kenke hau paeyaotaęž‰ homeke alemaęž‰ handaęž‰laęž‰me. Kutupa make IĚ±taęž‰ do kenke haunaęž‰taęž‰ homaęž‰ pa ulume hone witolome.
\v 15 Sekemesaisi hau pitaęž‰ sekemesaisi na pitaęž‰laęž‰ hau yaapotaęž‰ pa manda hau yaapoe. Otaęž‰ hau tieketaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ niki panake wandaęž‰hali mea haasaęž‰eki homeke otaęž‰ tumikiekie.
\v 16 Do hau telieleme wandaęž‰hali iki paęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ puki lopaasaęž‰eki pitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰eki yaapotaęž‰ iki ameĚ±leĚ± hao haenaęž‰e. Iki ameĚ±leĚ± make mo mandane Kodaęž‰naęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paeyao ameĚ±leĚ± make hao haenaęž‰e.
\p 
\v 17 Ya paeyaaso pitaęž‰ dupae. Maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ mandane kaęž‰ndaęž‰manu na kinaęž‰e. Pa ekipeke. Mo ya lokenaęž‰ hondo ulaęž‰eki manumaęž‰ walolotaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ Yesunaęž‰ pa hameke e pokaalo hali haloeki walaęž‰laęž‰me.
\p 
\v 18 Mo nikaęž‰ Tekehali Yesu Ketisonaęž‰ pa hameke aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ iki ya kametonu paeyao ameĚ±leĚ± hao haenaęž‰e. Kutu pinaęž‰e. 
